{"type": "article", "id": 22022, "title": "这些亚洲最棒酒店，预算充足的话可以考虑", "description": "有一种旅行爱好是酒店向旅行，只要有个好酒店，什么都可以。", "date": "2016-02-08T08:00:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 23216, "name": "海滨别墅"}, {"id": 667, "name": "酒店"}, {"id": 5729, "name": "度假"}, {"id": 6540, "name": "东南亚"}, {"id": 3070, "name": "泰国"}, {"id": 23217, "name": "半岛酒店"}], "category": 17, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 1218, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607031244115ZHRmFfCAljnBxiv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">最近，英国电讯报<a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/hotels/12129396/Best-hotels-in-Asia.html\"> Telegraph 的旅游版面评选出了亚洲最棒的几家酒店</a>，如果想就近度个假且预算充足的话，不妨考虑这个名单。<br></p>\n<h2>\n<a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/hotels/12129396/Best-hotels-in-Asia.html\">Iniala Beach House</a> @泰国<br>\n</h2>\n<p class=\"\">在泰国普吉岛的北方，<a href=\"http://www.iniala.com\">Iniala 海滨别墅酒店</a>就坐落在 Natai 海滩上。由三栋奢华别墅组成，每栋只有三间卧室，加上一套顶楼别墅、大片私人海滩区域——意味着不管你是独自、情侣档还是拖家带口的家庭旅行，都能享受到世外桃源的清静。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124400e1bCRozQA8G6iIKq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124400Cx2gYDWEA06dh8wH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124401PNFx43BOv1XsE02H.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031244019NAQdDnkhpvM1rZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">并且每一间都由来自不同国家的知名设计师、建筑师设计，巴西、泰国、西班牙、英国各国的风情也完美融入房间。大部分采用通透的设计，与外部海景融为一体。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">每栋别墅都标配私人司机、SPA 理疗师、管家、厨师 24 小时提供服务。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124402hAlUPgxyfWrXGdTO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124402Yr3DWcOIoeX0s2HN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>在这块只属于你的海边做做瑜伽、上上泰拳课——配有世界级的泰拳教练。并且全世界最年轻的西班牙米其林三星主厨Eneko Atxa 主持的餐厅也十分吸引人。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124403CeYgH8GOu0F45NIy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44363104\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>文华东方酒店 @日本东京</h2>\n<p class=\"\">东京的文华东方酒店（Mandarin Oriental）地处东京最繁华的商业地带，日本桥三井大厦的 30 层至 38 层（顶楼）。房间内的巨大落地窗拥有绝佳的视野，将城市天际线尽收眼底。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124403NG2cPnVKmSTq6dUv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124403WbtRnvgySUxEFZlD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure><p class=\"\"></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\" class=\"\"></figure><p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312440440ltGJECZwe8OmyA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56184211\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\" class=\"\">在 37 层极受好评的水疗中心可以做个冥想 SPA。并且除了能吃到正宗的高级日式料理，酒店内的粤菜馆、西班牙分子料理、法式大餐等全球美食精品餐厅也会满足吃货的心。</figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\" class=\"\"></figure><p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124404BEbMdDNowxOK0pZY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\" class=\"\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124405Nhjngac1OtqAGm0k.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<h2>\n<a href=\"http://www.comohotels.com/umaparo/\">UMA by COMO</a> @不丹</h2>\n<p class=\"\">作为 COMO 集团在不丹的第二处度假酒店，处在普那卡山谷（Punakha Valley）源头一片静谧之地。穿过天井庭院，就会看到覆盖着浓密树林的小山、阶梯状的稻田。</p>\n<p class=\"\">酒店呈古朴与奢华风格的结合，用上了石头、瓦片的精致木屋，功能齐全。各式传统艺术家的作品装饰特色的房间，比如来自尼泊尔的手编地毯、印度的棉质床上用品，都在呈现简洁的美学。有山中隐居理想的人不妨前来一试。对了，梁朝伟与刘嘉玲的婚礼也是在这里举办。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124405ZQm8q25zv9cUhnls.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58392435\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124406RFq1zw6Voypgu3ab.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53566959\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124406G7UbBXp13C0yNzDO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57033248\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124406ZWy9ndUFSiruL78A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59811828\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124407AMP7Qb9uJ0xwnLgX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58988016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>Alila Uluwatu @巴厘岛</h2>\n<p class=\"\">又是一处无敌的海景别墅，位于印度洋之上，巴厘岛宁静的布科（Bukit ）半岛。除了享受到壮阔沙滩和大海的景色，坐落在一块悬崖之上的鸟巢餐厅给人带来的感觉更是迷人。在巴厘岛这块区域，也是少数以极简风格示人的酒店。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124407cj0ehZRYImaTn7dL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60843373\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124408wdI2PvTGyREoLpcF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124408i16ItNpW7oS2BjQu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124409Nq0htusUnGO4x6zg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57526366\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031244094fE0l6rsdCh7DSz8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57124011\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<h2>奕居 @香港</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">从“弈居”（</span><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Upper House</span>）<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">这样独具东方气质的名字也可以对酒店的风格略知一二，设计师 </span><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andre Fu 的设计理念在于 “向上之旅”和家的宁静。位于太古广场的 38 层以上，每间房包括浴室都能够欣赏维港美景。</span></p>\n<p class=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031244105jB6bX3IGmoUTafC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5628866\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124410WnuiSJB4t52vxCoP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124411LEz5nrO60Wdkeu9j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031244111PyGgzFjpubRd8cv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0px;\" class=\"\"></figure>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"></figure><p></p>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n\n"}